textBody:
Ambient or Ambiance may refer to:

Music

*Ambient music
*Ambient 1–4, a set of four albums by Brian Eno, see Obscure Records
*Virgin Ambient series, by Virgin Records
*Ambient (album), by Moby
*Ambience (album), by the Lambrettas 
*Ambience (sound recording), also known as atmospheres or backgrounds

Other

*Ambient (desktop environment)
*Ambient (novel), a novel by Jack Womack
*Ambiancé (film), an upcoming experimental film by Swedish director Anders Weberg
*Mark Ambient, pen name of Harold Harley (1860–1937), English dramatist
